unit.name: 62 Volksgrenadier Division HQ
unit.History: Formed in Neuhammer Silesia as a replacement for the destroyed 62nd Infantry Division in September 1944 by redesignating the 583rd Volksgrenadier Division.

commander.Name: Friedrich Kittel
commander.PersBio: Friedrich Kittel was a lieutenant colonel on the staff of the Army Weapons Office at the start of the war. He commanded the 468th Infantry Regiment until 1942 when he returned to the staff of OKH. He assumed command of the 62nd Volksgrenadier Division on September 17, 1944.
